dct_title_s: Kyoto city bus travel map, Bus navi : 5 major sightseeing routes : Arashiyama area, Kinkakuji area, Okazaki area, Ginkakuji area, Higashiyama area / Kyoto Municipal Transportation Bureau. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Some buildings shown pictorially. Title from panel. "Kyoto Municipal Transportation Bureau, July 2006." Includes 4 insets of bus terminals, "City bus and subway information," and informatoin of Kyoto Municipal Transportation Bureau. Map of "5 major sightseeing routes," bus information, text, and color illustration on verso.
